## PublicApi

### Get Captcha Challenge
## Get Captcha Challenge
GET https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/captcha
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

### Get Countries
## Get Countries
GET https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/account/countries?fetchBy={{fetchBy}}
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

