### Complete OAuth Two-Factor Verification
## Complete OAuth Two-Factor Verification
PATCH https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/oauth
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "account_id": "<number>",
 "code": "<string>"
}


